Package game

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Alien
    Alien class holds information for each alien object, controls their location and movement, and determines size and image.
    Boss
    Boss class holds all infromation for bosses position, blasts, and how it is painted to screen.
    ControlsMenu
    This class generates Controls Menu.
    HighScoresMenu
    This class generates High Score Menu.
    MainGUI
    This class initiates the main gui frame and holds the components of the game.
    Meteor
    Meteor class holds information for each meteor object, controls their location and movement, and determines size and image.
    OrbitGame
    This class is the main game engine.
    Planet
    This class conatins data for backgroud planet, sets its position as it drifts across screen.
    PowerUp
    This class builds the power up object.
    ScorePanel
    This class initializes score panel and contains methods to update panel based on current score.
    Ship
    This class defines ship object and contains information on its location and firing status.
    StartMenu
    This class generates the start menu for the game.
    StatsMenu
    Stats menu displays the current users game stats.
    UpgradesMenu
    This menu has the upgrades options for the players ship.
    Utils
    Class contains utilities used in multiple classes.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    BlastTypes
    The different blast types for ship.
